{"tid":923022,"cid":6,"subCid":0,"title":"摩佬嘆難買入高水平球員","createTime":"2018-12-01T01:37:53.000Z","updateTime":"2018-12-01T05:54:50.000Z","uid":153600,"like":12,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":39,"replies":[{"pid":"00e6ae7bab83ae1233ab798f93249a83ac5d5100","tid":923022,"uid":153600,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-12-01T01:37:53.000Z","msg":"【<a href=\"http://now.com\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fnow.com&d=1puHGPAGbSmSENI0cD9hRozZXVCnaYNE8CBFJ%2F%2FgXXY%3D&h=a0179ec7\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">now.com</a>體育】曼聯領隊摩連奴指，現今想從別隊挖角引入高水平球員殊非易事，因為人家力足拒絕挖角。<br />\n<br />\n摩連奴在周末聯賽作客修咸頓前承認招攬高水平球員不易，並以熱刺作為例子。「我們可以從熱刺買入他們最出色的球員嗎？不，因為他們不會賣，或因為他們有力量可說不。」<br />\n<br />\n「數年前，誰是熱刺的最出色球員？卡域克。數年後，誰是他們的最佳球員？貝碧托夫。」以上兩人都被曼聯收歸旗下，惟他直言現在曼聯的挖角能力不能與以往相比：「現在我們可以去招納哈利卡尼、迪利阿里、艾歷臣（基斯甸艾歷臣）和孫興民？」<br />\n<br />\n「我們可以前往把這些傢伙帶來嗎？不。所以現在誰更具力量？是他們抑或我們？」轉會窗於元旦日重開，摩佬似暗示難有重大收購：「足球在變，要買入高、高、高水平的球員難多了。」<br />\n<br />\n修咸頓VS曼聯<br />\nNow621台02/12 01:30直播"},{"pid":"afe95a21d17cd5979bec201dc6f5e1ff2e0733a5","tid":923022,"uid":50744,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-01T01:43:07.000Z","msg":"買gtr着草算啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f738d19d3439b946cd4aa524ad4bbfd84791bf65","tid":923022,"uid":15830,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-12-01T01:44:27.000Z","msg":"山神呢<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9e19c72903a0aebc546a52f7690e33a136f6f927","tid":923022,"uid":97212,"like":6,"dislike":8,"score":-2,"quote":{"pid":"f738d19d3439b946cd4aa524ad4bbfd84791bf65","tid":923022,"uid":15830,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-12-01T01:44:27.000Z","msg":"山神呢<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-01T01:49:40.000Z","msg":"呀妓聽講係下遊隊 唔計"},{"pid":"ae56c6f5a173fef3bb5c1bceb79086d68aaebade","tid":923022,"uid":94771,"like":12,"dislike":0,"score":12,"citedBy":0,"replyTime"